<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("partials/head") -%>

  <body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar bg-light navbar-light navbar-expand-lg">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="navbar-brand"><img src="img/raccoon.png" alt="Logo" title="Logo" /></a>

        <button
          class="navbar-toggler"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#navbarResponsive"
        >
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
          <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/browse" class="nav-link">Browse</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/" class="nav-link active">About</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/events" class="nav-link">Events</a></li>
            <li class="nav-item"><a href="/communities" class="nav-link">Communities</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="navbar-nav">
            <li class="nav-item">
              <a href="/login" class="nav-link" style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.1rem"
                >Login/Register</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <!-- End Navigation -->

    <!-- Image Carousel -->

    <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="650000">
      <!-- Carousel Content -->

      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="img/carousel/tomatoes.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-8 bg-custom py-3 px-0">
                  <h1>Reducing food waste</h1>
                  <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-50 mx-auto my-3">
                    <h5 class="pd-3">
                      As of January 2020, UK households wasted 4.5 tonnes of food every year, which
                      is estimated to cost Â£14bn. However, many families are struggling and an
                      estimated 2.5 million children in the UK live in households without enough to
                      eat.
                    </h5>
                    <a href="https://wrap.org.uk/" style="color: #199e0fe0">wrap.org.uk/</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img src="img/carousel/books.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-8 bg-custom py-3 px-0">
                  <h1>Redistributing what we no longer need</h1>
                  <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-50 mx-auto my-3">
                    <h5 class="pd-3">
                      In the UK we throw away 31 million tonnes of rubbish each year. Some of this
                      will be useful. Books are particulary important. More than 380,000 children in
                      the UK do not own a single book.
                    </h5>
                    <a href="https://literacytrust.org.uk/" style="color: #199e0fe0"
                      >literacytrust.org.uk/</a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="img/carousel/vintage.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-8 bg-custom py-3 px-0">
                  <h1>Sharing within the community</h1>
                  <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-50 mx-auto my-3">
                    <h5 class="pd-3">
                      Using a website like this benefits everyone. We can share items with our
                      community gaining what we need and giving others what they need. We are
                      stronger together.
                    </h5>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="img/carousel/clothes.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-8 bg-custom py-3 px-0">
                  <h1>Slowing down fashion</h1>
                  <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-50 mx-auto my-3">
                    <h5 class="pd-3">
                      Around 350,000 tonnes of clothes go to landfill every year in the UK. More
                      waste, more clothing manufacture and more money spent on clothing. Why not
                      give away old clothes, or refresh your wardrobe with pre-loved items?
                    </h5>
                    <a href="https://traid.org.uk/" style="color: #199e0fe0">traid.org.uk/</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="img/carousel/toys.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-8 bg-custom py-3 px-0">
                  <h1>Giving items a second life</h1>
                  <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-50 mx-auto my-3">
                    <h5 class="pd-3">
                      A website aiming to give more life to items. From clothes to food and
                      furniture to nappies, together we can reduce waste.
                    </h5>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- End Carousel Content -->

      <!-- Previous & Next Buttons -->

      <a href="#carousel" class="carousel-control-prev" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="fas fa-chevron-left fa-3x"></span>
      </a>

      <a href="#carousel" class="carousel-control-next" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="fas fa-chevron-right fa-3x"></span>
      </a>

      <!-- End Previous & Next Buttons -->
    </div>

    <!-- End Image Carousel -->
    <div class="container-fluid bg-light">
      <!-- Three Column Section -->
      <div class="container bg-light">
        <div class="col-12 text-center mt-5 bg-light">
          <h1 class="text-dark pt-5">About us</h1>
          <div class="border-top border-primary d-none d-lg-block w-25 mx-auto my-3"></div>
          <p class="lead">What are we all about?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row my-5">
          <div class="col-md-6 my-4">
            <img src="img/1.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
            <h4 class="my-4">Sharing with others</h4>
            <p>
              We aim to reduce waste by encouraging people to give to what they no longer need. You
              can donate to local charities or local communities.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 my-4">
            <img src="img/3.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
            <h4 class="my-4">Giving and receiving close to home</h4>
            <p>
              Our location feature allows you to see if the items you are looking for are nearby.
              The map allows users to easily locate wanted goods.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 my-4">
            <img src="img/4.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
            <h4 class="my-4">Incentives to recycle</h4>
            <p>
              We also believe in the importance of recycling. Community initiatives encourage
              recycling of items and companies small and large offer incentives to recycle used
              packaging.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6 my-4">
            <img src="img/5.jpg" alt="" class="w-100" />
            <h4 class="my-4">Community matters</h4>
            <p>
              We believe that being green can be enjoyable for families and communities. Local
              competitions and initiatives between neighbourhoods and communities will reward
              recycling and bring people together.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Start Fixed Background IMG -->

    <div class="fixed-background">
      <div class="row text-light py-5">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h1>Get started</h1>
          <br />
          <br />
          <a href="/browse" class="btn btn-success btn-md ml-2">Start browsing</a>
          <a href="/communities" class="btn btn-success btn-md ml-2">Join some communities</a>
          <a href="/events" class="btn btn-success btn-md ml-2">Take part in an event</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="fixed-wrap">
        <div class="fixed"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer") -%>

    <!-- Script Source Files -->

    <!-- jQuery -->
    <script src="js/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Bootstrap 4.5 JS -->
    <script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Popper JS -->
    <script src="js/popper.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <script src="js/all.min.js"></script>

    <!-- End Script Source Files -->
  </body>
</html>
